Analysis of PDEs.summary:
  We prove local H\"older regularity for a nonlocal parabolic equations of the
form \begin{align*}
  \partial_t u + \text{P.V.}\int_{\mathbb{R}^N}
\frac{|u(x,t)-u(y,t)|^{p-2}(u(x,t)-u(y,t))}{|x-y|^{N+sp}}\,dy=0, \end{align*}
for $p\in (1,\infty)$ and $s \in (0,1)$.
